rismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104wov1665702821668.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wov1665702821668.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wov1665702821668.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"wov1665702821668\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      More Properties (Field Syntax)\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Enter additional syntax definitions for the field or modeled field syntax.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wov1665702821668__section_w12ab1b7b1_w13ab1b7_w14ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\"></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wov1665702821668__section_i4j_zz3_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1085179e60\">Fields</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"wov1665702821668__ul_tdr_zz3_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wov1665702821668__li_d3851e1_d3852e1_d3853e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"amp1665702821807.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/amp1665702821807.html\" title=\"The minimum number of subfield repetitions allowed in the field. The default assumes one repetition, that is, a field that contains no subfields.\">Minimum Field Repetition</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wov1665702821668__li_d3854e1_d3855e1_d3856e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gnc1665702821882.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gnc1665702821882.html\" title=\"The maximum number of subfield repetitions allowed in the field. The default assumes one repetition, that is, a field that contains no subfields.\">Maximum Field Repetition</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wov1665702821668__li_d3857e1_d3858e1_d3859e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"epp1665702821950.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/epp1665702821950.html\" title=\"Specify whether Uniface should check for matching parentheses, braces, and brackets in this field.\">Match Brackets</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wov1665702821668__li_d3860e1_d3861e1_d3862e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ryw1665702822019.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ryw1665702822019.html\" title=\"Specify whether all contiguous spaces in the field should be replaced by a single space.\">Replace Contiguous Spaces</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wov1665702821668__li_d3863e1_d3864e1_d3865e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fgv1665702614788.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fgv1665702614788.html\" title=\"Specify whether the bold character attribute is allowed for data in this field.\">Bold</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wov1665702821668__li_d3866e1_d3867e1_d3868e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mnq1665702616161.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mnq1665702616161.html\" title=\"Specify whether the italic character attribute is allowed for data in this field.\">Italic</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wov1665702821668__li_d3869e1_d3870e1_d3871e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fuo1665702822088.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fuo1665702822088.html\" title=\"Specify whether the underline character attribute is used for data in this field.\">Underline</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wov1665702821668__li_d3872e1_d3873e1_d3874e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zos1665702822168.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zos1665702822168.html\" title=\"Allow carriage return in this field. Applicable only to Unifields.\">Allow Carriage Return</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wov1665702821668__li_d3875e1_d3876e1_d3877e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lrp1665702822239.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lrp1665702822239.html\" title=\"Allow Gold characters in this field.\">Allow Gold Characters</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wov1665702821668__li_d3878e1_d3879e1_d3880e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lge1665702822307.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lge1665702822307.html\" title=\"The check digit algorithm used for checking data entered in the field.\">Check Digit Modulo</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wov1665702821668__li_d3881e1_d3882e1_d3883e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ywi1665702822380.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ywi1665702822380.html\" title=\"Specify whether Uniface deletes spaces, zeros, or control characters before the characters entered in the field.\">Delete ...</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8423892\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8423892\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopB